===非遊戲===
====媒體====
Oculus內含一個免費應用程式Oculus Cinema，讓Rift可以用來在虛擬電影院中觀看一般電影與影片，給予使用者在電影院觀看大螢幕的感受<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cnet.com/news/virtual-reality-and-the-silver-screen-a-match-made-in-heaven/ |title=CNET |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905091242/http://www.cnet.com/news/virtual-reality-and-the-silver-screen-a-match-made-in-heaven/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，亦有多家第三方公司開發虛擬戲院應用程式，供多位使用者在虛擬空間內觀看同一部電影<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hypergridbusiness.com/2014/07/riftmax-theater-is-a-multi-user-virtual-meeting-space/ |title=Hypergridbusiness.com |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905195340/http://www.hypergridbusiness.com/2014/07/riftmax-theater-is-a-multi-user-virtual-meeting-space/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

Rift還提供了觀看新類型之媒體的機會，這類媒體很難或根本不可能在一般的顯示器上觀看；如360度3D視訊，及「虛擬實境電影」。

環狀視訊（或稱360度視訊）僅能讓使用者轉動他們的頭部觀看，而Rift則開啟了立體環狀視訊（或稱360度3D視訊）的可能性。2014年9月，NextVR宣布該公司將使用價值20萬美元的攝影機，製造供Rift使用的360度3D內容，包括短片，以及運動賽事與演唱會等現場直播串流<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.roadtovr.com/nextvr-stereoscopic-360-degree-vr-cam-uses-180000-worth-of-red-6k-cameras/ |title=Roadtovr.com |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905205110/http://www.roadtovr.com/nextvr-stereoscopic-360-degree-vr-cam-uses-180000-worth-of-red-6k-cameras/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.slashgear.com/nextvr-aims-to-transform-sports-entertainment-forever-05372279/ |title=Slashgear.com |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924111631/http://www.slashgear.com/nextvr-aims-to-transform-sports-entertainment-forever-05372279/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年7月，Oculus宣布將與加拿大電影公司Felix & Paul Studios合作，製作Rift專用的360度3D視訊<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2015-07/17/oculus-rift-joins-felix-and-paul-vr-film-studios |title=Wired |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906024247/http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2015-07/17/oculus-rift-joins-felix-and-paul-vr-film-studios |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

Rift還支援新型態的娛樂體驗，Oculus稱之為「虛擬實境電影」。Oculus已成立Oculus Story Studio，以為Rift開發此類型之內容。該工作室有許多來自[[皮克斯動畫工作室|皮克斯動畫工作室]]與[[光影魔幻工業|光影魔幻工業]]等視覺特效公司的員工。Oculus Story Studio於[[2015年日舞影展|2015年日舞影展]]中展示該工作室的第一部虛擬實境電影《Lost》，獲得與會者的正面評價<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.engadget.com/2015/01/27/oculus-story-studio-is-the-pixar-of-virtual-reality/ |title=Engadget |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150829044141/http://www.engadget.com/2015/01/27/oculus-story-studio-is-the-pixar-of-virtual-reality/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://vimeo.com/117849907 |title=Vimeo |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150809140632/https://vimeo.com/117849907 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fastcompany.com/3041482/fast-feed/oculus-debuts-pixar-quality-virtual-reality-short-at-sundance-film-festival |title=Fastcompany.com |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924060822/http://www.fastcompany.com/3041482/fast-feed/oculus-debuts-pixar-quality-virtual-reality-short-at-sundance-film-festival |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

該工作室打算在Rift推出的同時推出5部虛擬實境短片，包括《Lost》、《Bullfighter》、《Henry》、《Dear Angelica》與《Kabloom》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.roadtovr.com/oculus-story-studio-promo-video-reveals-5-vr-short-films-works/ |title=Roadtovr.com |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905205157/http://www.roadtovr.com/oculus-story-studio-promo-video-reveals-5-vr-short-films-works/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====社交====
Oculus認為，長期來看，社交應用程式將成變最受歡迎的虛擬實境體驗<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://venturebeat.com/2014/03/25/zuckerberg-paints-a-surprising-future-for-oculus-vr-the-most-social-platform-ever/ |title=Venturebeat.com |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150919002409/http://venturebeat.com/2014/03/25/zuckerberg-paints-a-surprising-future-for-oculus-vr-the-most-social-platform-ever/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。許多供Rift使用的社交應用程式正在開發中，且預期會在此一產業中有激烈的競爭<ref name=X>{{Cite web |url=http://www.xconomy.com/san-francisco/2015/06/25/second-life-creator-linden-lab-prepares-to-test-parallel-vr-universe/ |title=Xconomy.com |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150827121533/http://www.xconomy.com/san-francisco/2015/06/25/second-life-creator-linden-lab-prepares-to-test-parallel-vr-universe |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年5月，AltspaceVR推出了他們的社交VR平臺的公測，供DK2的使用者測試。AltsapceVR讓人們可以居住在共享的虛擬空間裡，使用立體語音通訊，在虛擬螢幕上撥放來自網際網路的內容，與物件互動（允許下棋或其他棋類遊戲等活動），並支援眼球追縱與身體追縱等外加硬體<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://fortune.com/2015/05/20/altspacevr-social-vr/ |title=Fortune |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150824205349/http://fortune.com/2015/05/20/altspacevr-social-vr/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.npr.org/sections/alltechconsidered/2015/06/01/411233592/getting-physical-and-emotional-in-virtual-reality?utm_source=twitter.com&utm_campaign=alltech&utm_medium=social&utm_term=nprnews |title=NPR |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906113723/http://www.npr.org/sections/alltechconsidered/2015/06/01/411233592/getting-physical-and-emotional-in-virtual-reality?utm_source=twitter.com&utm_campaign=alltech&utm_medium=social&utm_term=nprnews |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年，[[第二人生|第二人生]]的創辦人[[Philip_Rosedale|Philip Rosedale]]離開了[[Linden實驗室|Linden實驗室]]，並創辦新的公司[[High_Fidelity|High Fidelity]]。該公司為Rift設計新的虛擬世界，將致力於將數以千計的使用者虛擬環境整合成一個一致的虛擬世界<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nwn.blogs.com/nwn/2013/10/philip-rosedale-leaves-linden-lab.html |title=NWM |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721192435/http://nwn.blogs.com/nwn/2013/10/philip-rosedale-leaves-linden-lab.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/5/19/5732386/high-fidelity-philip-rosendale-telepresence-second-life-hands-on |title=The Verge |accessdate=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2015-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907134458/http://www.theverge.com/2014/5/19/5732386/high-fidelity-philip-rosendale-telepresence-second-life-hands-on |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年5月，經營《[[第二人生|第二人生]]》的[[Linden實驗室|Linden實驗室]]宣布，他們也在開發新的虛擬世界，代號為Project Sansar，專為Rift與[[三星Gear_VR|三星Gear VR]]等虛擬實境頭套而設計。如同第二人生一般，Sansar將透過Linden的伺服器出租虛擬土地給其玩家，讓他們可以建造並販售虛擬物品與服務。Linden實驗室希望能於2016年底推出Sansar<ref name=X/>。

====工業/專業====
除了消費使用外，Rift也吸引了工業界與專業領域對於提高生產力、視覺化及廣告方面的興趣。

一些建築公司已將Rift用在視覺化與設計方面的實驗。使用合適的軟體，Rift可讓建築師看到他們的建築物實際上將變成怎麼，並得到一些在傳統顯示器上無法瞭解的資訊<ref>{{cite news |author=Scott Hayden |title=HoloLens App Envisions Immersive Future for Architecture and Construction |url=http://www.roadtovr.com/hololens-app-envisions-immersive-future-architecture-construction/ |publisher=Road to VR |date=2015-05-06 |accessdate=2015-09-18 |archive-date=2015-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707042240/http://www.roadtovr.com/hololens-app-envisions-immersive-future-architecture-construction/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年初，[[奧迪|奧迪]]開始在在專賣店使用Rift DK2，以協助其客戶配置他們感興趣的車子，並觀看賽車時車子裡看到的景象<ref>{{cite news |author=Chris Bruce |title=Audi reveals virtual reality 'dealership in a briefcase' |url=http://www.autoblog.com/2015/01/19/audi-reveals-virtual-reality-dealership-in-a-briefcase/ |publisher=Autoblog.com |date=2015-01-19 |accessdate=2015-09-18 |archive-date=2015-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918151404/http://www.autoblog.com/2015/01/19/audi-reveals-virtual-reality-dealership-in-a-briefcase/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Gillian West |title=Audi partners with Somo to create fan experiences using Google Glass and Oculus Rift at Goodwood Festival of Speed |url=http://www.thedrum.com/news/2014/06/26/audi-partners-somo-create-fan-experiences-using-google-glass-and-oculus-rift |publisher=Thedrum.com |date=2014-06-26 |accessdate=2015-09-18 |archive-date=2016-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203172107/http://www.thedrum.com/news/2014/06/26/audi-partners-somo-create-fan-experiences-using-google-glass-and-oculus-rift |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[挪威陸軍|挪威陸軍]]已開始利用Rift DK2進行實驗，以讓裝甲車輛駕駛員與指揮官能有最好的[[状态意识|状态意识]]能力<ref>{{cite news |author=Russell Brandom |title=The Norwegian Army is using the Oculus Rift to drive tanks |url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/5/5/5682942/the-norwegian-army-is-using-the-oculus-rift-to-drive-tanks |publisher=The Verge |date=2014-05-05 |accessdate=2015-09-18 |archive-date=2015-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150920023110/http://www.theverge.com/2014/5/5/5682942/the-norwegian-army-is-using-the-oculus-rift-to-drive-tanks |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

